1.project structure :
crm_data_accuracy/
├── crm_data_accuracy.py       # Main Python script
├── crm_customers.csv          # Sample input data
├── requirements.txt           # Python dependencies
└── README.md                  # Project documentation

2.Features
✅ Email & Phone Number Validation

✅ Missing Value Imputation using KNNImputer

✅ Anomaly Detection with Isolation Forest

✅ Export Cleaned Data to .xlsx or .csv


3.Add-On: Interactive Dashboard with Streamlit
This will let you:

Upload a CRM file

View validation results

Explore anomalies visually

Download cleaned data
